	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=120740><span id=Scholar>ayere</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>27 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.24]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Word drops are completely random. They drop off mob's within 5 levels of the spell you are trying to research. You'll hear rumor that &quot;mob xxx drops word yyy&quot;. It doesn't. It's random.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
