	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=64677><span id=Sage>xaanru</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>1713 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>evil eyes in gorge of king xorbb drop polished bone bracelts. should be easy kill at 37. Just watch out for the charm spell. If you use a pet, It will be charmed, and used against you, unless you fearkite the evil eye, and kill it fast.<br><br>Great Oowomp (sp?) in Timorous Deep drops a variety of nice items. It MIGHT be possible for you to solo there, especially if you pick up some mage summoned pet weapons.<br><br>Flowing black robe drops in Najena. You could get one at your level, WITH a group. I doubt you could solo this.<br><br>Also, golden ear studs are a quest in Qeynos. +3 int earring. The gelatinous cube (cubert) that you need to kill is very low level, but is a somewhat rare spawn with a placeholder. You also have to have decent faction to do the quest. Hail the quest giver, and see if he will give it to you.</p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
