	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=64677><span id=Sage>xaanru</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>1713 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [4.90]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>At 19, bandits in PC is about the best exp in the game.<br><br>Stein of maggok is an awesome item for 200pp or so. <br><br>Crystalline, blackened crystalline, or robe of the oracle can all be had for 200 occasionally. Maybe a little more. Also batskull earring is very nice for 200. Buy one nice thing, not a ton of crap you'll just replace in 4 levels anyway.<br><br>If you like the necro, don't give his stuff away. Usually, its best to wait until you have at least one character thats higher level (50+ preferred, at LEAST 35, before twinking alts).<br><br>Also, for even more quick cash, kill spiderlings/spiders and loot the silks, take them to the bazaar and sell for several plat each. Some spiders can drop 4-8 silks in one kill, and the silks average 3-5pp each and 2-4 for spiderlings, which you can kill with your pet, as fast as you can target them and say attack.<br><br>Also, cat,bear,wolf and rockhopper hides sell well in the bazaar.<br><br></p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
